Name: extrahepatic bile duct small cell adenocarcinoma
Definition: An uterine corpus leiomyomatosis that is located throughout the uterine corpus.
Synonym: Oat cell extrahepatic bile duct carcinoma

Name: obsolete autosomal recessive polycystic kidney
Definition: An uterine corpus leiomyomatosis that is located throughout the uterine corpus.

Name: papillary extrahepatic bile duct adenocarcinoma
Definition: A benign perivascular tumor that is characterized as a vascular variant of a glomus tumor.
